# Module scaffold: Spark{MODULE_NAME}

Replace `{MODULE_NAME}` with PascalCase feature name. **Only** under `Packages/Spark{MODULE_NAME}/` (never `Spark/Features/`).

## Package layout

```
Packages/Spark{MODULE_NAME}/
  Package.swift
  Sources/Spark{MODULE_NAME}/
    Domain/
      Models/
      UseCases/
      {MODULE_NAME}Repository.swift
    Data/
      DTOs/
      Mock{MODULE_NAME}Repository.swift
      Live{MODULE_NAME}Repository.swift   // or {MODULE_NAME}Repository+Live.swift
    Presentation/
      {MODULE_NAME}RootView.swift
      {MODULE_NAME}ViewModel.swift
  Tests/Spark{MODULE_NAME}Tests/
```

## Requirements

- **Repository protocol** in Domain; **Mock + Live** in Data
- **UseCase** per operation; typed `{MODULE_NAME}Error: LocalizedError` when needed
- **ViewModel**: `@MainActor` `@Observable`; UseCases only — no `URLSession` / Keychain in VM
- **View**: `#Preview` — loading, loaded, empty, error; `String(localized:defaultValue:comment:)`
- **Navigation**: tab root → `SparkScreenContainer`; push flow → outer `NavigationStack` + `embedding: .none` ([ARCHITECTURE.md](../../docs/ARCHITECTURE.md))
- **UI**: [DESIGN_PHILOSOPHY.md](../../docs/DESIGN_PHILOSOPHY.md) — no decorative controls; chevron only if row navigates
- New HTTP routes → [API_CONTRACT.md](../../docs/API_CONTRACT.md) first

## App wiring

1. Add local package to `Spark.xcodeproj`
2. Register in `CompositionRoot` (Mock vs Live)
3. `@Environment` or constructor injection from `ContentView` / `SparkAppShell`

## Before PR

```bash
make check && make lint && make test-packages
```

## Checklist

- [ ] No singletons
- [ ] Sendable DTOs / domain models
- [ ] Cancellation in `.task`
- [ ] `make check-ui` passes
